name: tiss_env_favicon
description:
A developer tool to distinguish between the TISS environments by setting different favicons.
TISS - Technical University of Vienna Information Systems and Services
css:
@namespace url(http://www.mozilla.org/keymaster/gatekeeper/there.is.only.xul);

/*
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A developer tool to distinguish between the TISS environments by setting different favicons.

TISS - Technical University of Vienna Information Systems and Services

by lual 2016-04-20
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Respect to:
  *  maxoku 
     https://userstyles.org/users/303311
     https://userstyles.org/styles/124152/google-old-favicon
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Notes:
  *  How to generate the background-url-data from a file with rubyonrails:
     Base64.strict_encode64(open("/home/fg/data/bdln/tiss_favicons_variationen/tissrot1616.ico") { |io| io.read })
  *  https://www.w3.org/TR/css3-selectors/#attribute-substrings
  *  how to checkout firefox-xul-css-selectors:
     https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Tools/Browser_Toolbox
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*/

/*
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  localhost: change favicon to tiss_klein_grau_s.ico
*/
#identity-icon[src*='0.0.0.0:3'][src*='favicon'],
#PopupAutoCompleteRichResult .autocomplete-richlistitem .ac-site-icon[src*='0.0.0.0:3'][src*='favicon'],
.site .site-favicon[src*='0.0.0.0:3'][src*='favicon'],
.menu-iconic-icon[src*='0.0.0.0:3'][src*='favicon'],
.bookmark-item .toolbarbutton-icon[src*='0.0.0.0:3'][src*='favicon'],
.tab-icon-image[src*='0.0.0.0:3'][src*='favicon'],
#identity-icon[src*='localhost:3'][src*='favicon'],
#PopupAutoCompleteRichResult .autocomplete-richlistitem .ac-site-icon[src*='localhost:3'][src*='favicon'],
.site .site-favicon[src*='localhost:3'][src*='favicon'],
.menu-iconic-icon[src*='localhost:3'][src*='favicon'],
.bookmark-item .toolbarbutton-icon[src*='localhost:3'][src*='favicon'],
.tab-icon-image[src*='localhost:3'][src*='favicon']
{
  padding-left: 16px !important;
  background: url(data:image/x-icon;base64,) !important; }

/*
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  test: change favicon to tiss_klein_gruengruen_s.ico
*/
#identity-icon[src*='test.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'],
#PopupAutoCompleteRichResult .autocomplete-richlistitem .ac-site-icon[src*='test.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'],
.site .site-favicon[src*='test.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'],
.menu-iconic-icon[src*='test.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'],
.bookmark-item .toolbarbutton-icon[src*='test.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'],
.tab-icon-image[src*='test.tiss.tuwien.ac.at']
{
  padding-left: 16px !important;
  background: url(data:image/x-icon;base64,) !important; }

/*
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  dev1: change favicon to tiss_klein_hellbl_s.ico
*/
#identity-icon[src*='dev1.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
#PopupAutoCompleteRichResult .autocomplete-richlistitem .ac-site-icon[src*='dev1.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.site .site-favicon[src*='dev1.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.menu-iconic-icon[src*='dev1.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.bookmark-item .toolbarbutton-icon[src*='dev1.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.tab-icon-image[src*='dev1.tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon']
{
  padding-left: 16px !important;
  background: url(data:image/x-icon;base64,) !important; }


/*
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  prod: change favicon to tissrot1616.ico
*/
#identity-icon[src^='https://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
#PopupAutoCompleteRichResult .autocomplete-richlistitem .ac-site-icon[src^='https://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.site .site-favicon[src^='https://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.menu-iconic-icon[src^='https://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.tab-icon-image[src^='https://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],

#identity-icon[src^='http://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
#PopupAutoCompleteRichResult .autocomplete-richlistitem .ac-site-icon[src^='http://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.site .site-favicon[src^='http://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.menu-iconic-icon[src^='http://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.tab-icon-image[src^='http://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],

#identity-icon[src^='tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
#PopupAutoCompleteRichResult .autocomplete-richlistitem .ac-site-icon[src^='tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.site .site-favicon[src^='tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.menu-iconic-icon[src^='tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],
.tab-icon-image[src^='tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon'],

.bookmark-item .toolbarbutton-icon[src^='moz-anno:favicon:https://tiss.tuwien.ac.at'][src*='favicon']
{
  padding-left: 16px !important;
  background: url(data:image/x-icon;base64,) !important; }
